reviews.author: Gabriela Rosas
reviews.text: Be careful with the sacristan, Carlos. At the church door, I tried to take a photo, and a man named Carlos yelled at me and attacked me, trying to take my cell phone away, struggling with me, telling me that taking photos at the door was prohibited. There was no sign saying it was prohibited, and the way he did it was offensive and aggressive; he seemed like someone with mental problems. Be careful with your children. If he treats an adult like that, what can he do to the children who sometimes enter churches jumping and playing? I hope someone from the municipality gives him a psychological exam; people like that are dangerous when they're in close contact with people.
